{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"unique-users","title":"unique-users","subLink":null},{"id":"storingnestedentityvalues","title":"Storing Nested Entity Values","subLink":[]},{"id":"storingmutipleskillsusingformarray","title":"Storing Mutiple Skills Using FormArray","subLink":[]},{"id":"getfileobject","title":"Get File Object","subLink":[]},{"id":"errormessage","title":"ErrorMessage","subLink":[]},{"id":"conditionalvalidation","title":"Conditional Validation","subLink":[]},{"id":"whatwebuilt","title":"What we Built","subLink":[]}],"title":"Nested Properties","description":"","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"simple","gitDocPath":"https://github.com/rxweb/rxweb.io/edit/master/docs/angular/learn/advance/unique-users.md","category":"learn","subCategory":"","linkTitle":"nested-props","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= 'storingnestedentityvalues'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Storing Nested Entity Values<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#storingnestedentityvalues'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The userdetails form is having an address info formGroup which is constructed for the purpose to store the value of city, state, areaName etc. we will start making a reactive form with fields of firstName, lastName and email and create a nested reactive form for the fields which are related to the adress entity. We will create a form with the use of RxFormGroup.  </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"advance-forms-complete-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'storingmutipleskillsusingformarray'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Storing Mutiple Skills Using FormArray<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#storingmutipleskillsusingformarray'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Moving further with our UserDetails form by adding a field of skillName into the reactive form such that each value entered into the input should be unique. In this case we will make the use of <a class=\"redirect-link\"  href=\"/form-validations/unique/validators\">unique</a> validator. </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"advance-forms-formarray-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'getfileobject'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Get File Object<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#getfileobject'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >For the profilePhoto field we have applied the built-in image validator we will further enhance it by converting it into formData with the help of <span class='highlighted'>toFormData()</span> method provided by <span class='highlighted'>RxFormGroup</span>. </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"advance-forms-fileobject-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'errormessage'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>ErrorMessage<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#errormessage'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Displaying the error messages in a better way to globally resolve the validation messages and show the error messages without writing multiple <span class='highlighted'>*ngIf</span> conditions in the html of the component.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"advance-forms-errormessage-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'conditionalvalidation'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Conditional Validation<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#conditionalvalidation'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >In the cases where we want to fire a validation based upon some user's selected value. Here we fire the required validation on the address formGroup based upon the <span class='highlighted'>isPermanentAddress</span> set to true.       </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"advance-forms-conditionalvalidation-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'whatwebuilt'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>What we Built<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/learn/nested-props/validators#whatwebuilt'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<img src=assets/rxwebcore/Images/advance-form-user.PNG alt='Creating Projects'>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}